videos.headline: Michigan State RB breaks through the pile for TD
videos.description: Michigan State RB Elijah Collins is caught up for only a moment but is then able to punch it in for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play ( Michigan State RB breaks through the pile for TD ) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lewerke throws TD pass under pressure
